data.eml:eml: A new species of iguana Brachylophus Cuvier 1829 (Sauria: Iguania: Iguanidae) from Gau Island, Fiji Islands

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Fisher, Robert N., Niukula, Jone, Watling, Dick, Harlow, Peter S. (2017): A new species of iguana Brachylophus Cuvier 1829 (Sauria: Iguania: Iguanidae) from Gau Island, Fiji Islands. Zootaxa 4273 (3): 407-422, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4273.3.5
